<li id="cite_note-15"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFSlide2004">Slide, Anthony (2004). <i><a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=Ng_fyVJVMz4C" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=Ng_fyVJVMz4C" rel="nofollow">American Racist: The Life and Films of Thomas Dixon</a></i>. University Press of Kentucky. pp.&#160;p.102. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0813123283" class="internal">ISBN 0813123283</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=Ng_fyVJVMz4C" class="external free" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=Ng_fyVJVMz4C" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.com/books?id=Ng_fyVJVMz4C</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=American+Racist%3A+The+Life+and+Films+of+Thomas+Dixon&amp;rft.aulast=Slide&amp;rft.aufirst=Anthony&amp;rft.au=Slide%2C+Anthony&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3Bp.102&amp;rft.pub=University+Press+of+Kentucky&amp;rft.isbn=0813123283&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DNg_fyVJVMz4C&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:The_Birth_of_a_Nation"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ol>
